---
const navItems = [
	{ label: "Trang chủ", href: "#top", icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="size-4"><path d="m3 11 9-8 9 8"/><path d="M5 10v10h14V10"/><path d="M10 20v-6h4v6"/></svg>` },
	{ label: "Về KIGI", href: "#about", icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="size-4"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>` },
	{ label: "Dịch vụ", href: "#services", icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="size-4"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 22h8"/><path d="M12 18v4"/><path d="m8 9 2.2 2.2L8 13.4"/><path d="M14 13h3"/></svg>` },
	{ label: "Quy trình", href: "#workflow", icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="size-4"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>` },
	{ label: "Dự án", href: "#projects", icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="size-4"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>` },
	{ label: "Liên hệ", href: "#contact", icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="size-4"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.8 19.8 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6A19.8 19.8 0 0 1 2.1 4.18 2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.35 1.89.66 2.77a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.1 9.9a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.3-1.22a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.88.31 1.81.53 2.77.66A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>` },
];
---
<footer class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#e0f2fe]/90 to-[#f0f9ff]/90 text-slate-600 border-t border-[#02b3fd]/20">
	<div class="section-shell py-16">
		<!-- Banner Footer (Gradient rực rỡ bóng bẩy phối màu mới) -->
		<div class="mb-12 grid gap-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[#215abd] via-[#568fca] to-[#02b3fd] p-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_.8fr] lg:p-12 shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(2,179,253,0.2)] border border-white/20 relative overflow-hidden">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-white to-transparent"></div>
			<div class="relative z-10 text-white">
				<p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/90">KIGI Agency</p>
				<h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-extrabold md:text-4xl text-white">Sẵn sàng nâng cấp vị thế thương hiệu?</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/80">
					Liên hệ ngay với KIGI Agency để được tư vấn thiết kế Website chất lượng cao cùng gói dịch vụ truyền thông tối ưu doanh số.
				</p>
			</div>
			<!-- Đồng bộ nút trong Banner (Nút chính & Nút phụ đồng bộ 52px) -->
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-end relative z-10">
				<a class="btn-premium-outline !bg-white !text-[#02b3fd] !border-0 hover:!bg-slate-100 shadow-lg" href="tel:0563555535">Gọi điện ngay</a>
				<a class="btn-premium-outline !bg-transparent !text-white !border-white hover:!bg-white hover:!text-[#02b3fd]" href="mailto:info@kigiagency.com">Gửi Email</a>
			</div>
		</div>
 
		<!-- Links Grid -->
		<div class="grid gap-12 border-b border-[#02b3fd]/10 pb-12 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
					<img src="/logo.jpg" alt="KIGI Agency Logo" class="h-10 w-auto rounded-lg object-contain shadow-sm border border-[#02b3fd]/10" />
					<div>
						<p class="text-xl font-black tracking-wider text-deep-navy">KIGI</p>
						<p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#02b3fd]">Agency</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
					Đối tác tin cậy thiết kế Website chuẩn SEO và triển khai các giải pháp Marketing trực tuyến hiệu quả.
				</p>
			</div>
 
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-deep-navy">Menu nhanh</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
					{navItems.map((item) => (
						<li>
							<a class="hover:text-[#02b3fd] transition-colors" href={item.href}>{item.label}</a>
						</li>
					))}
				</ul>
			</div>
 
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-deep-navy">Dịch vụ cốt lõi</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
					<li>Thiết kế Website UI/UX chuẩn SEO</li>
					<li>Quản lý Fanpage và sáng tạo content</li>
					<li>Chạy quảng cáo Facebook / Google / TikTok</li>
					<li>Sản xuất video ngắn Reels / TikTok</li>
					<li>Tư vấn nhận diện thương hiệu</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
 
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-deep-navy">Liên hệ trực tiếp</h3>
				<div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
					<p class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="font-bold text-deep-navy shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap">Hotline:</span> 0563.555.535
					</p>
					<p class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="font-bold text-deep-navy shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap">Email:</span> info@kigiagency.com
					</p>
					<p class="flex items-start gap-2">
						<span class="font-bold text-deep-navy shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap">Địa chỉ:</span> Số 25 - 26 Nguyễn Đình Chiểu, Phường Vĩnh Phước, TP. Nha Trang, Tỉnh Khánh Hòa
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
 
		<!-- Bottom Footer Bar -->
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 pt-8 text-sm text-slate-500 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
			<p>© 2026 KIGI Agency. All rights reserved.</p>
			<div class="flex gap-6">
				<a class="hover:text-[#02b3fd] transition-colors" href="#">Chính sách bảo mật</a>
				<a class="hover:text-[#02b3fd] transition-colors" href="#">Điều khoản sử dụng</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
